---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { strings } from '../../i18n/strings';
const t = strings.en;
---
<BaseLayout lang="en" title={`Privacy Policy | ${t.brand}`} description="How we handle your data on nevnap.app — GDPR-compliant policy." altLangPath="/privacy">
  <article class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl pt-12 md:pt-16">
    <nav class="text-sm text-zinc-500" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 list-none"><li><a href="/en/" class="hover:text-primary-500">{t.brand}</a></li><li aria-hidden="true">›</li><li aria-current="page" class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Privacy Policy</li></ol>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight"><span class="gradient-text">Privacy Policy</span></h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-500">Last updated: January 1, 2026.</p>

    <section class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">1. Data Controller</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Renátó Bogár (sole individual operator, hereinafter "Operator") informs users (hereinafter "You" / "User") about the data processing practices of the nevnap.app website and NévnapTárX mobile application.</p>
        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:bogarrenato@gmail.com" class="text-primary-500 underline">bogarrenato@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">2. What data do we collect?</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">The website does <strong>not collect personally identifiable information</strong> from non-registered visitors. The following technical data is processed automatically:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>IP address (anonymized — last octet masked)</li>
          <li>Browser type, version, operating system</li>
          <li>Pages visited, time spent</li>
          <li>Referrer page</li>
          <li>Device type (mobile/desktop)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">3. Purpose and legal basis</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Traffic analytics</strong> (GDPR Art. 6(1)(f) — legitimate interest): service improvement.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookie management</strong> (GDPR Art. 6(1)(a) — consent): via the cookie banner.</li>
          <li><strong>Ad serving</strong> (future feature): solely based on user's explicit consent.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">4. Data Processors</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We engage the following third-party processors:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Cloudflare, Inc.</strong> (USA) — web hosting, CDN.</li>
          <li><strong>Google LLC</strong> (USA) — Google Analytics (anonymized).</li>
          <li><strong>Google Ireland Ltd.</strong> — future AdSense (only with consent).</li>
          <li><strong>Apple Inc.</strong> and <strong>Google LLC</strong> — App Store, Google Play (mobile app only).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">5. Data retention</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Analytics data: 14 months</li>
          <li>Cookie preferences: 12 months (localStorage)</li>
          <li>Server logs (Cloudflare): max 30 days</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">6. Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Under GDPR, every user has the right to:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Access</strong> — what data we store</li>
          <li><strong>Rectification</strong> — correcting inaccurate data</li>
          <li><strong>Erasure</strong> ("right to be forgotten")</li>
          <li><strong>Restriction of processing</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Data portability</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Object</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> at any time</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">To exercise any right, email <a href="mailto:bogarrenato@gmail.com" class="text-primary-500 underline">bogarrenato@gmail.com</a>. We respond within <strong>30 days</strong>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">7. Filing a complaint</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">You may file a complaint with the Hungarian Data Protection Authority (NAIH):</p>
        <address class="mt-2 not-italic">1055 Budapest, Falk Miksa utca 9-11. Hungary<br/><a href="https://www.naih.hu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary-500 underline">www.naih.hu</a></address>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">8. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">See our <a href="/en/cookies" class="text-primary-500 underline">Cookie Policy</a> for details.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">9. Changes</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">This policy may be updated. Significant changes are announced on the website. The update date is at the top.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
